140.4	Singleton_pattern	Singleton pattern	Alternatively, the inner class Singletonholder can be also substituted by implementing a Property which provides also access to the static final/readonly class members. Just like the lazy object in C#, whenever the Singleton.Instance Property is called, this singleton is instantiated for the very first time.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fb/Singleton_UML_class_diagram.svg/250px-Singleton_UML_class_diagram.svg.png
